           <div class="middlebox"><span class="middleboxTitle">Learn how we collect and use our visitors personal information</span><br/><br/>
               PaymentWorld takes privacy and data protection issues seriously.  We have designed this Privacy Policy to explain how we handle personally 
               identifiable information collected from merchants who register for services and submit information to PaymentWorld through the Internet.<br /><br />
